# NWScript

## Event chain

```
mod_on_load.nss → evt_module.nss → inc_bootstrap.nss (Bootstrap_Init)
evt_on_enter.nss → evt_client.nss (login, validation, quests)
evt_on_leave.nss → evt_client.nss (session save, audit)
```

Wire new module events through `evt_*` dispatchers, not directly in `mod_*` stubs.

## Includes

- Utility: `#include "inc_*"` from `src/scripts/`
- DB layer: `#include "inc_db_*"` from `src/scripts/include/db/`
- Keep `include/` for libraries only — not entry-point scripts.

## Compile loop

```bash
bash tools/compile-scripts.sh
# or MCP: nwn.script.compile / nwn.script.diagnostics
```

Fix `file:line` diagnostics before committing. Compiled `.ncs` goes to `build/ncs/` (git-ignored).

## Style

- One responsibility per script file; match existing naming in the directory.
- Campaign DB in `inc_db_core.nss` is intentional — do not "fix" by switching to NWNX SQL unless asked.
